"推"},{"pid":"d34cb05f55a18462be568d5879559942b61c8f50","tid":2095353,"uid":233338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:35:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ca0471d7df651bd966ad3f5f9d6985d52083564","tid":2095353,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3f46361ca12b65046c202cab8b5c5d37b2d1d51","tid":2095353,"uid":331739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:45:38.000Z","msg":"即係你去到都可以打麻雀 但唔係好似公屋咁打開到門 上下兩層都聽到你碰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:36:21.000Z","msg":"好鍾意你既例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0514070c1800a2b31109f874e14353855715ce","tid":2095353,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d4308be3f937a3b4f90635ee23b0595b52aa0d1","tid":2095353,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T18:07:14.000Z","msg":"如果一個大陸新移民話自己係香港人，又是一個中國人，一般情況下連登仔係點睇？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:42:36.000Z","msg":"有乜野問題<br />\n但係如果佢係為中國人利益做野，做間諜，或者做一D係中國容許但係香港唔容許既野<br />\n例如冇公德心，唔尊重他人，貪污，靠關係上位，壓榨欺凌<br />\n<br />\n正如如果香港人去到外國又炒樓、睇唔起冇錢冇讀書既低下階層、冇同情心+冷漠<br />\n人地都唔會想要你"},{"pid":"68b7e6b22a94512bd853759f40da38af7c5c61cf","tid":2095353,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:48:11.000Z","msg":"推上去推上去推上去推上去"},{"pid":"2dec2305a7242cbca8823eed559fce25f3602753","tid":2095353,"uid":268429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:52:16.000Z","msg":"條女好索..可唔可以帶我走呀.利申BNO Holder 願意付出..每日十次."},{"pid":"8d8d87b8e32681151e5e4b47f60a5102bbd6e817","tid":2095353,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:52:48.000Z","msg":"推上去推上去推上去推上去"},{"pid":"e461d09ae2bff37a9e1398bc2a4fbaee2051d903","tid":2095353,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:54:11.000Z","msg":"aggrr"},{"pid":"da1ac1892aa64aae5a57676132c9922a9fe1c7e3","tid":2095353,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc